---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Getting Help With Goma">
  <section class="page-hero compact">
    <p class="eyebrow">Support</p>
    <h1>Get help from the Goma community</h1>
    <p>
      Use the manual for reference material and GitHub Discussions for usage
      questions, troubleshooting, and community support.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card-grid resource-cards">
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h2>Documentation and Tutorials</h2>
      <p>Reference manuals, beginners material, and legacy tutorial PDFs are collected on the documentation page.</p>
      <a class="text-link" href="/documentation.html">Open documentation</a>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h2>GitHub Discussions</h2>
      <p>General usage questions and answers should be directed to the Goma GitHub Discussions board.</p>
      <a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/goma/goma/discussions">Ask on GitHub Discussions</a>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
      <h2>Community Wiki</h2>
      <p>The community wiki is available on GitHub for shared notes and project information.</p>
      <a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/goma/goma/wiki">Open community wiki</a>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
